fields.name: TRIBECA FILM FESTIVAL | EVENTS | APPLE STORE PANEL: TRIBECA FILM/Movie FESTIVAL SNEAK PEEK
fields.Description: Join the annual Tribeca Film Festival Sneak Peek to get a glimpse of the exciting new work by some of our TFF 2014 filmmakers. We'll be showing never-before-seen clips and speaking with the directors of some of the festival's most highly anticipated world premieres including Summer of Blood (Onur Tukel), Ballet 422 (Jody Lee Lipes), An Honest Liar (Justin Weinstein), Below Dreams (Garrett Bradley), and Match (Stephen Belber). The Sneak Peek is a great way to get a preview of all the films premiering at this year's festival.

fields.name: Float-A-Boat on the scenic upper Duck river
fields.Description:
Come out and float the beautiful, scenic upper Duck River in Bedford county, Tn! This part of the river is rated a class 1 and is perfect for both beginners and experienced paddlers! It is a peaceful, scenic float that you will encounter many types of fish, mussels, and wildlife! There are kayaks, canoes, and tubes available for rent. Shuttle is also available for your own personal boats. We also have SUP boards and paddle boats available for Normandy lake!

Hosting Individual or Organization Name: Float-A-Boat, LLC

Does this event take place on a National Scenic, Historic or Recreation Trail?: No

Special Directions to Site: 10 miles off I-24 exit 97 toward Wartrace

Activity 1: Paddling Trip

Activity 1 Mileage Traveled or Maintained: 3-15 miles

Activity 1 Special Instructions: Reservations required to guarantee availability...Walk-ins welcome but not guaranteed....Open 7 days a week depening on weather and conditions of river....Call or e-mail... walk-ins welcome on weekends
